        "id": 5255
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-03-10T16:27:45Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The dox for duplicate say \"The returned stream will be positioned at the beginning of its data.\" Wouldn\u0027t that be 0 (rather than fOriginalOffset)? rewind() rewinds to 0, so it seems like we are treating that as the beginning of data.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 219,
        "startChar": 42,
        "endLine": 219,
        "endChar": 57
      },
      "revId": "e61ca4daeac8d8461846051bd854e31b754bb9bb",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": true
