      "writtenOn": "2017-03-10T16:48:47Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m actually in favor of changing rewind. The reality is that there is one caller who wants a SkFILEStream which starts at a non-0 location, and they would prefer that rewind go back to the original offset. I could leave this alone for now to avoid changing behavior.",
      "parentUuid": "feaf5acc_36599eb2",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 219,
        "startChar": 42,
        "endLine": 219,
        "endChar": 57
      },
      "revId": "e61ca4daeac8d8461846051bd854e31b754bb9bb",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
